    <entry>
      <title>Hexo博客(主题Buttetfly)更换电脑后快速配置</title>
      <link href="2021/03/07/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2-%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98Buttetfly-%E6%9B%B4%E6%8D%A2%E7%94%B5%E8%84%91%E5%90%8E%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/"/>
      <url>2021/03/07/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2-%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98Buttetfly-%E6%9B%B4%E6%8D%A2%E7%94%B5%E8%84%91%E5%90%8E%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>1.备份原电脑中如下文件</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scaffolds&#x2F;#模板文件</span><br><span class="line">source&#x2F;#资源文件，主要是文章</span><br><span class="line">themes&#x2F;butterfly&#x2F;source&#x2F;img&#x2F;#主题下图片资源夹</span><br><span class="line">_config.butterfly.yml#主题配置文件</span><br><span class="line">_config.yml#配置文件</span><br><span class="line">.gitignore</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>![Hexo更换电脑 01_2021-03-07_11-49-27](D:\Users\29490\Pictures\hexo用图\Hexo博客-主题Buttetfly-更换电脑后快速配置\Hexo更换电脑 01_2021-03-07_11-49-27.png)</p><p>![Hexo更换电脑 02_2021-03-07_11-50-22](D:\Users\29490\Pictures\hexo用图\Hexo博客-主题Buttetfly-更换电脑后快速配置\Hexo更换电脑 02_2021-03-07_11-50-22.png)</p><p>2.新电脑上安装Git与Node.js</p><p>3.安装hexo</p><p>输入命令</p><p><code>npm install hexo-cli -g</code></p><p>初始化hexo</p><p><code>hexok init </code></p><p>安装依赖包</p><p><code>npm install</code></p><p>4.安装插件</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1.搜索插件</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-search --save</span><br><span class="line">2.字数统计、阅读时长插件</span><br><span class="line">npm i --save hexo-wordcount</span><br><span class="line">3.部署上传插件</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>5.用备份文件替换对应文件</p><p>6.输入命令<code>hexo s</code>，测试是否正常</p><p>7.生成SSH，添加到Github</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1.设置Github用户名与电子邮箱地址</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.name &quot;yourname&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email &quot;youremail&quot;</span><br><span class="line">2.查看用户名&#x2F;用户邮箱地址设置，检查是否正确</span><br><span class="line">git config user.name</span><br><span class="line">git config user.email</span><br><span class="line">3.生成SSH</span><br><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;youremail&quot;</span><br><span class="line">4.查看SSH</span><br><span class="line">ssh -T git@github.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
